573
00:36:22,000 --> 00:36:22,950
What should we do then?

574
00:36:23,230 --> 00:36:25,020
Just give him a bit more time.

575
00:36:25,320 --> 00:36:26,600
If he really can't handle it well,

576
00:36:26,710 --> 00:36:27,890
I'll step in.

577
00:36:28,030 --> 00:36:30,110
I'll cover the legal fees.

578
00:36:30,360 --> 00:36:31,010
As for the lawyer,

579
00:36:31,070 --> 00:36:32,460
I've also found the most suitable one.

580
00:36:32,490 --> 00:36:34,550
The one who helped me with labor disputes before.

581
00:36:34,840 --> 00:36:36,690
Please trust Wanghe's character.

582
00:36:36,760 --> 00:36:38,880
He has never hurt anyone since childhood.

583
00:36:38,910 --> 00:36:39,670
So you can rest assured.

584
00:36:39,670 --> 00:36:41,640
How can I possibly rest assured?

585
00:36:42,630 --> 00:36:44,380
You two are childhood friends.

586
00:36:44,410 --> 00:36:45,280
If it really comes down to it,

587
00:36:45,320 --> 00:36:47,030
how can you possibly stand on our side?

588
00:36:47,060 --> 00:36:47,850
Stop it.

589
00:36:47,940 --> 00:36:48,560
Stop it.

590
00:36:51,670 --> 00:36:52,400
Mom.

591
00:36:53,360 --> 00:36:54,880
I used to listen to you in everything,

592
00:36:55,850 --> 00:36:57,080
but not this time.

593
00:36:58,020 --> 00:36:59,230
Tianming has passed away.

594
00:36:59,850 --> 00:37:01,530
With so many troubles at home,

595
00:37:01,560 --> 00:37:03,040
and the children are still so young,

596
00:37:03,550 --> 00:37:04,960
how can I possibly put all my hopes

597
00:37:04,980 --> 00:37:06,900
on the two of them?

598
00:37:10,550 --> 00:37:11,230
Fenghua.

599
00:37:12,550 --> 00:37:14,030
I know you're a righteous and responsible person.

600
00:37:14,770 --> 00:37:16,240
You have a kind heart.

601
00:37:16,260 --> 00:37:18,280
You've also done a lot for our family.

602
00:37:18,610 --> 00:37:19,850
I appreciate your kindness.

603
00:37:21,850 --> 00:37:24,130
But I must seek justice for Tianming's death.

604
00:37:24,490 --> 00:37:26,140
Even if I have to risk my life,

605
00:37:26,170 --> 00:37:27,980
I won't let them off the hook!

606
00:37:29,680 --> 00:37:30,550
Lirong.

607
00:37:30,760 --> 00:37:31,490
Lirong.

608
00:37:31,620 --> 00:37:32,500
Lirong!

609
00:37:34,010 --> 00:37:37,090
[Beijing Haidian Kejing Garden]

610
00:37:42,820 --> 00:37:43,630
No!

611
00:37:43,670 --> 00:37:44,410
Stop!

612
00:37:45,710 --> 00:37:46,880
What's going on here?

613
00:37:45,980 --> 00:37:47,050
[R.I.P.]

614
00:37:49,880 --> 00:37:51,420
Give my son back!

615
00:37:51,230 --> 00:37:51,940
[R.I.P.]

616
00:37:54,070 --> 00:37:55,400
Mom!

617
00:37:59,060 --> 00:38:01,630
My son is gone!

618
00:38:01,650 --> 00:38:02,520
Hey.

619
00:38:02,800 --> 00:38:03,540
You two.

620
00:38:03,670 --> 00:38:05,550
Whatever this is for, can't we talk in the office?

621
00:38:05,550 --> 00:38:07,110
Why should I talk to you?

622
00:38:07,110 --> 00:38:09,110
Get your boss here!

623
00:38:09,110 --> 00:38:10,000
Watch your tone.

624
00:38:10,000 --> 00:38:11,090
This is Mr. Song.

625
00:38:11,230 --> 00:38:12,350
Mr. Song, is it?

626
00:38:12,630 --> 00:38:14,260
What do you want to do?

627
00:38:14,280 --> 00:38:15,420
No, no, no.

628
00:38:16,440 --> 00:38:17,820
The boss you're referring to,

629
00:38:17,850 --> 00:38:19,840
is it the head of Haidian operations?

630
00:38:19,860 --> 00:38:22,860
Whoever is responsible for Tianming, that's who I'm looking for.

631
00:38:23,240 --> 00:38:24,900
If you don't take responsibility,

632
00:38:24,920 --> 00:38:26,190
I'll die here today!

633
00:38:26,190 --> 00:38:27,260
Me too!

634
00:38:33,270 --> 00:38:34,450
Don't go too far.

635
00:38:34,480 --> 00:38:35,740
Get out of my way!

636
00:38:35,840 --> 00:38:36,640
Remember,

637
00:38:36,670 --> 00:38:38,380
no physical conflicts allowed!

638
00:38:38,800 --> 00:38:39,580
Got it.

639
00:38:39,710 --> 00:38:41,480
I want to see your boss!

640
00:38:41,630 --> 00:38:43,400
I want to see your boss!

641
00:38:52,940 --> 00:38:53,950
What are you all doing?

642
00:38:55,690 --> 00:38:56,590
It's no big deal.

643
00:39:03,920 --> 00:39:04,870
Why are you panicking?

644
00:39:07,220 --> 00:39:08,840
I'm here, aren't I?

645
00:39:09,320 --> 00:39:10,510
All these years,

646
00:39:10,590 --> 00:39:12,370
what haven't we been able to overcome?

647
00:39:12,720 --> 00:39:14,040
Listen up, everyone.

648
00:39:14,510 --> 00:39:16,380
Before this matter is resolved,

649
00:39:16,670 --> 00:39:19,360
no one is allowed to post anything on Weibo

650
00:39:19,400 --> 00:39:20,500
or WeChat Moments!

651
00:39:26,580 --> 00:39:27,350
Brother-in-law.

652
00:39:31,800 --> 00:39:33,970
Brother-in-law, you see?

653
00:39:33,990 --> 00:39:35,360
What a mess

654
00:39:35,360 --> 00:39:36,190
they've caused in the company.

655
00:39:36,190 --> 00:39:37,110
We can't let them keep causing trouble like this.

656
00:39:37,110 --> 00:39:38,550
Otherwise, the impact will be too negative.

657
00:39:38,550 --> 00:39:39,800
Why should you be worried?

658
00:39:40,960 --> 00:39:42,970
Who they want to see is Xie Wanghe.

659
00:39:43,440 --> 00:39:44,320
Besides,

660
00:39:45,230 --> 00:39:46,670
the bigger this gets, the better.

661
00:39:47,410 --> 00:39:48,250
Anyway,

662
00:39:50,230 --> 00:39:52,090
we won't be the ones taking the blame in the end.

663
00:39:53,240 --> 00:39:54,440
Brother-in-law.

664
00:39:54,630 --> 00:39:57,630
If this gets too big, it'll end badly for everyone.

665
00:40:00,550 --> 00:40:02,050
It all comes down to money.

666
00:40:02,330 --> 00:40:05,000
If money can solve it, it's not a problem.

667
00:40:05,110 --> 00:40:06,400
Brother-in-law, if this really blows up,

668
00:40:06,400 --> 00:40:08,000
Mr. Meng will definitely step in personally

669
00:40:08,030 --> 00:40:09,070
to protect Xie Wanghe.

670
00:40:10,890 --> 00:40:13,300
That depends on how big it gets.

671
00:40:16,290 --> 00:40:19,410
What if the situation gets so serious

672
00:40:19,780 --> 00:40:22,340
that Meng has to sacrifice a "rook" to save the "king"?

673
00:40:26,670 --> 00:40:28,790
Brother-in-law, I'll contact the media right now.

674
00:40:28,850 --> 00:40:29,460
Come back.

675
00:40:32,480 --> 00:40:33,720
No need to rush it.

676
00:40:34,150 --> 00:40:35,180
Let them continue to make a scene.

677
00:40:38,290 --> 00:40:40,460
Netizens will definitely take photos and post it on Weibo.

678
00:40:40,590 --> 00:40:41,700
Once this matter

679
00:40:41,800 --> 00:40:42,820
becomes a trending topic on Weibo,

680
00:40:43,350 --> 00:40:45,410
when Meng is out of options,

681
00:40:45,440 --> 00:40:47,250
we'll add fuel to the fire.

682
00:40:47,270 --> 00:40:49,250
Fan the flames a bit.

683
00:40:50,480 --> 00:40:53,760
This time, we'll let that brat Xie Wanghe

684
00:40:53,840 --> 00:40:56,350
spit out everything he took from us before.

685
00:40:57,340 --> 00:40:58,910
Every last bit of it.

686
00:41:05,290 --> 00:41:05,850
Brilliant.

687
00:41:07,800 --> 00:41:09,040
Absolutely brilliant.

688
00:41:09,690 --> 00:41:10,580
Brother-in-law.

689
00:41:11,250 --> 00:41:13,100
My sister couldn't have made a better choice when she chose you

690
00:41:13,150 --> 00:41:15,460
back then.

691
00:41:15,530 --> 00:41:18,370
What nonsense are you talking about?

692
00:41:19,550 --> 00:41:21,360
Brother-in-law, but I just told them

693
00:41:21,390 --> 00:41:23,140
not to post on Weibo

694
00:41:23,190 --> 00:41:24,550
or WeChat Moments.

695
00:41:24,550 --> 00:41:26,190
Was that a mistake?

696
00:41:27,680 --> 00:41:29,160
Can you possibly control all of that?

697
00:41:29,190 --> 00:41:30,220
If they want to post it, let them be.

698
00:41:30,630 --> 00:41:31,270
You're right.

699
00:41:31,730 --> 00:41:33,570
It's in human nature. The more you tell them not to post,

700
00:41:33,670 --> 00:41:35,190
the more likely they'll do it.

701
00:41:38,030 --> 00:41:39,480
Alright, get back to work.

702
00:41:39,990 --> 00:41:42,410
I'll make arrangements for tonight then.

703
00:41:42,950 --> 00:41:45,120
Don't worry. I won't let my sister know.

704
00:41:52,830 --> 00:41:54,610
You know He Tianming, right?

705
00:41:53,080 --> 00:41:57,490
[Fenghua Express]

706
00:41:54,740 --> 00:41:55,920
Yes, we were colleagues.

707
00:41:56,120 --> 00:41:57,630
Can you describe what kind of person he was?

708
00:41:57,630 --> 00:41:58,550
He was a nice person.

709
00:41:58,550 --> 00:42:00,190
We worked together every day.

710
00:42:00,210 --> 00:42:01,210
So you worked together...

711
00:42:01,240 --> 00:42:01,840
Yes.

712
00:42:01,840 --> 00:42:02,450
We

713
00:42:02,480 --> 00:42:03,740
all worked at this station.

714
00:42:03,910 --> 00:42:04,700
Is the work tiring?

715
00:42:05,040 --> 00:42:05,440
Yes, it's tiring.

716
00:42:05,440 --> 00:42:06,150
In our line of work,

717
00:42:06,190 --> 00:42:07,800
it's quite hard anyway.

718
00:42:07,800 --> 00:42:08,670
Fenghua.

719
00:42:09,430 --> 00:42:10,210
Who are they?

720
00:42:10,750 --> 00:42:11,730
Reporters.

721
00:42:14,490 --> 00:42:16,170
You're Ms. Xia, right?

722
00:42:17,310 --> 00:42:18,210
I am.

723
00:42:18,230 --> 00:42:20,080
Hello, we're reporters from Fellow Workers.com.

724
00:42:18,960 --> 00:42:22,340
[Fenghua Express Notice Board]

725
00:42:20,190 --> 00:42:21,120
We heard about what happened to He Tianming,

726
00:42:21,150 --> 00:42:22,190
and we're here for an interview.

727
00:42:22,400 --> 00:42:23,400
Who sent you here?

728
00:42:23,630 --> 00:42:25,000
We came on our own initiative.

729
00:42:25,150 --> 00:42:25,960
He Tianming's case

730
00:42:25,980 --> 00:42:27,430
isn't an isolated incident in the food delivery industry.

731
00:42:27,480 --> 00:42:28,630
So we wanted to use this opportunity

732
00:42:28,710 --> 00:42:30,480
to speak up for vulnerable groups.

733
00:42:31,110 --> 00:42:32,150
You're asking the wrong person.

734
00:42:32,150 --> 00:42:32,950
What we do is parcel delivery,

735
00:42:33,070 --> 00:42:33,590
not food delivery.

736
00:42:33,630 --> 00:42:34,480
Yes, I know.

737
00:42:34,590 --> 00:42:36,370
But he worked here before, right?

738
00:42:36,480 --> 00:42:38,550
And I heard you felt quite sorry when he left.

739
00:42:38,550 --> 00:42:40,440
So we want to ask what happened at that time.

740
00:42:40,480 --> 00:42:42,630
We're not at liberty to discuss matters related to the food delivery industry.

741
00:42:43,670 --> 00:42:44,630
From now on,

742
00:42:45,110 --> 00:42:46,490
without my permission,

743
00:42:46,630 --> 00:42:48,450
whoever gives an unauthorized interview

744
00:42:48,840 --> 00:42:50,480
will receive a serious demerit. Do you understand?

745
00:42:50,480 --> 00:42:51,420
Understood!

746
00:42:51,510 --> 00:42:52,150
Hello.

747
00:42:52,150 --> 00:42:53,590
Please leave. We are not accepting interviews anymore.

748
00:43:01,910 --> 00:43:02,730
Fenghua.

749
00:43:03,160 --> 00:43:03,910
Fenghua.

750
00:43:04,920 --> 00:43:05,910
Are you alright?

751
00:43:06,960 --> 00:43:07,600
I'm okay.
